comments: Payton II (POR) is already in Brooks' (MEM) path and does not deliver contact.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) legally contests Lillard's (POR) jump shot attempt.
Bane (MEM) and Payton II (POR) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Simons (POR) avoids making contact with Morant's (MEM) arm as he is gathering the ball.
Lillard (POR) legally contests Brooks' (MEM) jump shot attempt.
Clarke (MEM) brings his hands towards Hart (POR) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away to secure the rebound.
Hart (POR) extends his forearm into Clarke's (MEM) body and initiates contact that affects his shot attempt.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) makes clean contact with the ball as he attempts to tie up Eubanks (POR).
Brooks (MEM) brings his arm forward towards Eubanks (POR) and marginal contact occurs as Brooks' hand simultaneously makes contact with the ball.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court (defensive goaltending) was confirmed.  Morant (MEM) makes contact with the ball after it has reached its apex and has started its downward flight to the rim.
Hart (POR) and Clarke (MEM) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs on the perimeter.
Eubanks (POR) legally contests Jackson Jr.'s (MEM) jump shot attempt.
Lillard (POR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Clarke (MEM).
Jackson Jr. (MEM) extends his arms into Eubanks (POR) and delivers contact as he defends the shot attempt.
Payton II (POR) extends his forearm into Morant's (MEM) side and contact occurs prior to Morant's upward shooting motion.
Hart (POR) extends his left arm forward and makes contact with Morant's (MEM) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Bane (MEM) is moving alongside Payton II's (POR) path and marginal contact occurs in the backcourt.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) commits a take foul on Lillard (POR).
Payton II (POR) and Morant (MEM) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
Brooks (MEM) does not inbound the ball within five seconds.
Brooks (MEM) and Lillard (POR) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
